{"tid":1998285,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特：Tim Cook 花了數小時教他用 iPhone 11","createTime":"2020-05-02T09:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T14:30:01.000Z","uid":22822,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b14ecea430ae3df5adb8b29755a2426a59185b","tid":1998285,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:38:50.000Z","msg":"今年二月，巴菲特表示終放棄用了多年，價值僅為 20 美元的 Samsung U320 翻蓋式功能手機，換成 iPhone 11。89 歲的他開始學習使用，暫時只將它視為電話，不像其他人一般使用到 iPhone 眾多的功能。<br />\n<br />\n近日，他接受 Yahoo! 財經的訪問時透露，Tim Cook 花了數小時教他用 iPhone 11，他笑言經指導後他的 iPhone 使用能力提升至 2 歲小孩程度。<br />\n<br />\n不過，在出訪問期間巴菲特竟然沒有帶他的 iPhone 同時「出席」，他解釋怕有電話打擾訪問（似乎他暫時未懂得用勿擾功能）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KU8kxz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKU8kxz9.png&h=4946614f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pi1FxAt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpi1FxAt.png&h=fe363bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">股神親自示範俾你睇，如果你買咗一啲你唔了解嘅公司業務嘅股票嘅下場</span></span>"},{"pid":"c2ed15be8b3dc5d083ac6149c0b3caa27a8b2e31","tid":1998285,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"廢老又發癲"},{"pid":"ea013fa0ccfe68df321986333318e08067d6d61c","tid":1998285,"uid":304281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"Tim Cook心諗：鬼叫你係股東咩"},{"pid":"b187201cb28374ff3442c388c637a725a7a52f1e","tid":1998285,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"紅字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />字"},{"pid":"f724eba6df29f75415d93ac4c4410d3976f2be42","tid":1998285,"uid":120499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:58:46.000Z","msg":"AAPL 廢老輸咗啲嘜<img sr